a10acfe7-d405-43fb-a272-f3c6ef59cc4b	4475d406-4e5a-484b-8a99-d10c625c6ebc	Welcome to Internship Program 2026	We are excited to welcome all interns and mentors to the 2026 internship program. Please ensure you complete your onboarding tasks within the first week.	all	2026-03-29 21:34:16.473356
