ebcd1c34-a2df-4a7d-9124-47cc72fe3b64	4475d406-4e5a-484b-8a99-d10c625c6ebc	Mentor Evaluation Guidelines	Mentors are requested to evaluate assigned interns weekly and submit feedback through the portal.	mentors_only	2026-03-29 21:34:16.473356
23e34c89-e051-4712-97e8-f57dfa99fa36	f2e41f92-86da-47f1-9563-d07321742030	Holiday Notice	The office will remain closed on account of a public holiday this Friday. Attendance will not be required.	all	2026-03-29 21:34:16.473356
b9f1bf00-9c6c-4097-b60b-3cebe0dbcaeb	f2e41f92-86da-47f1-9563-d07321742030	AI/ML Training Session	A special training session on AI and Machine Learning will be conducted this Saturday at 11 AM in the seminar hall.	interns_only	2026-03-29 21:34:16.473356
b7fcbccf-3d20-4a6d-a93e-2695c5cdd9fc	4475d406-4e5a-484b-8a99-d10c625c6ebc	Monthly Mentor Meeting	All mentors are requested to attend the monthly sync meeting scheduled on Monday at 4 PM.	mentors_only	2026-03-29 21:34:16.473356
3b46267a-3926-4e15-8062-94fc4039e31d	f2e41f92-86da-47f1-9563-d07321742030	Project Submission Deadline	All interns must submit their project reports before the end of this month. Late submissions will not be accepted.	interns_only	2026-03-29 21:34:16.473356
